<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ف ح م:</span> <span class="c2">(الْفَحْمُ)</span> مَعْرُوفٌ الْوَاحِدَةُ <span class="c2">(فَحْمَةٌ)</span> وَقَدْ يُحَرَّكُ مِثْلُ نَهْرٍ وَنَهَرٍ.<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>قَدْ قَاتَلُوا لَوْ يَنْفُخُونَ فِي فَحَمْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَ <span class="c2">(الْفَحِيمُ)</span> أَيْضًا الْفَحْمُ. وَ <span class="c2">(فَحْمَةُ)</span> الْعَشَاءِ ظُلْمَتُهُ. وَشَعْرٌ <span class="c2">(فَاحِمٌ)</span> أَيْ أَسْوَدُ. وَ <span class="c2">(فَحَّمَ)</span> وَجْهَهُ <span class="c2">(تَفْحِيمًا)</span> سَوَّدَهُ. وَ <span class="c2">(أَفْحَمَهُ)</span> أَسْكَتَهُ فِي خُصُومَةٍ أَوْ غَيْرِهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>